  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Arunachal Pradesh</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Arunachal has extreme climate variation — tropical lowlands, temperate valleys and alpine highlands. October to April is ideal for most areas: Tawang is spectacular in October-November (after monsoon) and March-April (spring flowers); Ziro is beautiful year-round; Namdapha is best November-April. All visitors require an Inner Line Permit (ILP) before entering.</p>
