{emoji:"🌿",name:"Cane & Bamboo Craft",location:"Statewide — Every Tribal District",desc:"Bamboo is the primary material of everyday life in Arunachal Pradesh — every tribe has its own bamboo craft vocabulary. Chang houses (bamboo stilted homes), fishing traps, carrying baskets (zurung), water containers, cooking vessels, musical instruments, bridges and sleeping mats are all made from bamboo. The precision of Arunachali bamboo weaving — some baskets are watertight — represents accumulated knowledge of extraordinary depth."}
